	"keywords": "Serverless, javascript, Web Development, Nodejs, Tech",
	"description": "What a mouthful of a title. Wouldn’t you agree? In this walkthrough you’ll learn\nabout securing your Serverless endpoints with JSON web tokens.\n\nThis will include a basic setup of a Serverless REST API with a few endpoints,\nand of course an authorizer function. This authorizer will act as the middleware\nfor authorizing access to your resources.\n\nDuring the creation process, we’ll use the Serverless framework\n[https://serverless.com/] for simulating a development environment just like\nyou’re used",
